msgid "Lemmy Plugins"
msgstr ""

#: src/contributors/08-plugins.md:3
msgid ""
"Plugin support will be added in the upcoming 1.0 release. You can already "
"start developing plugins now."
msgstr ""

#: src/contributors/08-plugins.md:5
msgid "Follow these steps:"
msgstr ""

#: src/contributors/08-plugins.md:7
msgid ""
"Follow the normal [setup instructions](/docs/administration/administration."
"html), using `:nightly` tags to get the latest development version."
msgstr ""

